### Broadcast Dashboard Summary
GET http://localhost:8081/api/broadcasts/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Broadcast Dashboard History (paged, optional search)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/broadcasts/dashboard/history?search={{search}}&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Broadcast Dashboard History - with search example
GET http://localhost:8081/api/broadcasts/dashboard/history?search=reminder&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
